track_notes: Mountain hike without climbing or ladders. Limited parking space in Ebnit. Starting point can also be reached well by public transport.
Alpine hike with a few ladders and a bit of easy climbing just before the summit. Paid parking at the starting point.
To reach this summit you must come up an iron ladder. A bit of risk that make you excited and satisfied on the top.
track_title: Class EE  Long iron flight of steps   2 summits RING Track
